837330818, \"rank\": 0.098329629357955, \"text\": \"Qin\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Qin_dynasty\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Qin_dynasty\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Peaty's evening swim\", \"from\": 1769, \"to\": 1789}, {\"ngram\": \"an improvement\", \"from\": 1794, \"to\": 1808}, {\"ngram\": \"0.32 seconds\", \"from\": 1812, \"to\": 1824}, {\"ngram\": \"his morning effort\", \"from\": 1828, \"to\": 1846}, {\"ngram\": \"neither he\", \"from\": 1852, \"to\": 1862}, {\"ngram\": \"the kind\", \"from\": 1891, \"to\": 1899}, {\"ngram\": \"times\", \"from\": 1903, \"to\": 1908}, {\"ngram\": \"the past\", \"from\": 1938, \"to\": 1946}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Brit's world record stands at almost two seconds quicker and while that was set fback in 2019, both he and Qin - the second-fastest man in history - have broken the 58-second barrier this year.\", \"from\": 1949, \"to\": 2146, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2060, \"end\": 2063, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Qin_dynasty\", \"score\": 0.9028381837330818, \"rank\": 0.098329629357955, \"text\": \"Qin\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Qin_dynasty\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Qin_dynasty\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Brit's world record\", \"from\": 1949, \"to\": 1972}, {\"ngram\": \"the second-fastest man\", \"from\": 2066, \"to\": 2088}, {\"ngram\": \"history\", \"from\": 2092, \"to\": 2099}, {\"ngram\": \"the 58-second barrier\", \"from\": 2114, \"to\": 2135}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There have been suggestions that the relatively shallow depth of the pool at Paris's La Defense Arena will mean fast times are hard to come by at these Games but Peaty says that will not matter come Sunday night's final.\", \"from\": 2148, \"to\": 2368, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2225, \"end\": 2230, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 4.887992786574411e-13,